title: Canzoniere (Project Vinland)
description:
You can find chapters for Canzoniere by Souryou Fuyumi translated by scanlation group Project Vinland here.

Synopsis: Cesare Borgia, the most beautiful hero in the history of the Renaissance. The story depicts Cesare's first and last love, which oscillated like a flame for a moment between history.
author: Souryou Fuyumi
